***********************************************************
This Readme gives graphical picture of the simpler samples:
***********************************************************

unitsimplex_xy.ply

2
| \
0- 1

************************

square_xz.ply

3 - 2
| /	|
0 - 1

************************

square_with_int_point_xy.ply

4  -  3
|\	 /|
|  0  |
|/   \|
1  -  2

************************

hexagon_xy.ply

	3 - 2
   / \ / \
  4 - 0 - 1
   \ / \ /
	5 - 6

************************

pyramid_xy.ply

4  -  3
|\	 /|
|  0  |
|/   \|
1  -  2
	
where 5 has z-coordinate 1, the rest has 0

*************************

mountain_xy.ply

8  -  7  -  6  -  5
|\	 / \   / \   /|
|  9  -  10 -  0  |
|/   \ /   \ /   \|
1  -  2  -  3  -  4
	
where 9,10,11 have z-coordinate 1, the rest has 0

**************************

random_square_xy.ply

11 -22 ... 121
|			|
...	*		
| \	 		...
2 - 13
| \	 | \	|
1 - 12 ... 111

with 0 on boundary and random in interior

